 want much inside flexion or bend in this exercise.", "tokens": [50384, 407, 291, 500, 380, 528, 709, 1854, 5896, 313, 420, 11229, 294, 341, 5380, 13, 50728], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15568648904993915, "compression_ratio": 1.5923566878980893, "no_speech_prob": 0.01158804539591074}, {"id": 47, "seek": 26290, "start": 270.17999999999995, "end": 277.29999999999995, "text": " Simplify it and just allow them to be straight in the exercise.", "tokens": [50728, 3998, 564, 2505, 309, 293, 445, 2089, 552, 281, 312, 2997, 294, 264, 5380, 13, 51084], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15568648904993915, "compression_ratio": 1.5923566878980893, "no_speech_prob": 0.01158804539591074}, {"id": 48, "seek": 26290, "start": 277.29999999999995, "end": 280.62, "text": " In the canter, it's the same exercise.", "tokens": [51084, 682, 264, 393, 391, 11, 309, 311, 264, 912, 5380, 13, 51250], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15568648904993915, "compression_ratio": 1.5923566878980893, "no_speech_prob": 0.01158804539591074}, {"id": 49, "seek": 26290, "start": 280.62, "end": 286.02, "text": " Bring the air up into your collarbones to make the canter smaller so that the right", "tokens": [51250, 12842, 264, 1988, 493, 666, 428, 20672, 44954, 281, 652, 264, 393, 391, 4356, 370, 300, 264, 558, 51520], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15568648904993915, "compression_ratio": 1.5923566878980893, "no_speech_prob": 0.01158804539591074}, {"id": 50, "seek": 28602, "start": 286.34, "end": 294.29999999999995, "text": " front foot is landing shorter and then it's landing longer.", "tokens": [50380, 1868, 2671, 307, 11202, 11639, 293, 550, 309, 311, 11202, 2854, 13, 50778], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11617063547109628, "compression_ratio": 1.572192513368984, "no_speech_prob": 0.053098488599061966}, {"id": 51, "seek": 28602, "start": 294.29999999999995, "end": 299.06, "text": " It's the same as the trot exercise.", "tokens": [50778, 467, 311, 264, 912, 382, 264, 504, 310, 5380, 13, 51016], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11617063547109628, "compression_ratio": 1.572192513368984, "no_speech_prob": 0.053098488599061966}, {"id": 52, "seek": 28602, "start": 299.06, "end": 308.02, "text": " There's a lot of big benefits to having this ability with your horse to move them around", "tokens": [51016, 821, 311, 257, 688, 295, 955, 5311, 281, 1419, 341, 3485, 365, 428, 6832, 281, 1286, 552, 926, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11617063547109628, "compression_ratio": 1.572192513368984, "no_speech_prob": 0.053098488599061966}, {"id": 53, "seek": 28602, "start": 308.02, "end": 309.02, "text": " with your breath.", "tokens": [51464, 365, 428, 6045, 13, 51514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11617063547109628, "compression_ratio": 1.572192513368984, "no_speech_prob": 0.053098488599061966}, {"id": 54, "seek": 28602, "start": 309.02, "end": 314.74, "text": " And one of them is when you're doing a lateral movement like you just saw, you can open and", "tokens": [51514, 400, 472, 295, 552, 307, 562, 291, 434, 884, 257, 25128, 3963, 411, 291, 445, 1866, 11, 291, 393, 1269, 293, 51800], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11617063547109628, "compression_ratio": 1.572192513368984, "no_speech_prob": 0.053098488599061966}, {"id": 55, "seek": 31474, "start": 314.74, "end": 321.26, "text": " close the movement simply with your breath and the maintenance of your legs and arms", "tokens": [50364, 1998, 264, 3963, 2935, 365, 428, 6045, 293, 264, 11258, 295, 428, 5668, 293, 5812, 50690], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11613596718886803, "compression_ratio": 1.5914634146341464, "no_speech_prob": 0.021310631185770035}, {"id": 56, "seek": 31474, "start": 321.26, "end": 329.90000000000003, "text": " doing a lot of other things does not have to interfere with the going forward and back.", "tokens": [50690, 884, 257, 688, 295, 661, 721, 775, 406, 362, 281, 23946, 365, 264, 516, 2128, 293, 646, 13, 51122], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_